 "data": "@startmindmap
* Data Science Roadmap
** Computer Science Fundamentals
*** Understand how computers work (CPU, RAM, input/output devices).
*** Learn about binary representation and data storage.
** Programming Basics
*** Get hands-on experience with basic coding concepts.
*** Explore programming languages (Python, R, etc.).
** Data Manipulation
*** Dive into Numpy and Pandas for data cleaning and transformation.
*** Explore data visualization tools (Matplotlib, Seaborn).
** Statistics and Mathematics
*** Understand essential math concepts (linear algebra, calculus, probability).
*** Learn about statistical methods used in data science.
** Machine Learning
*** Explore supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms.
*** Understand model evaluation and hyperparameter tuning.
** Deep Learning
*** Study neural networks, backpropagation, and activation functions.
*** Explore deep learning frameworks (TensorFlow, PyTorch).
** Data Engineering
*** Learn about databases (SQL, NoSQL).
*** Understand data pipelines and ETL processes.
** Big Data Technologies
*** Explore tools like Hadoop, Spark, and Hive.
*** Understand distributed computing and parallel processing.
** Cloud Computing
*** Learn about cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, Azure).
*** Understand how to deploy and scale data science applications.
** Domain Knowledge
*** Gain expertise in specific domains (finance, healthcare, etc.).
*** Understand business context and problem-solving.
** Communication and Visualization
*** Learn how to present findings effectively.
*** Explore data storytelling and dashboards.
** Continuous Learning
*** Stay updated with the latest trends and technologies.
*** Participate in online courses, conferences, and communities.
@endmindmap
